@startuml
title Viaverse Chat / Messaging — Activity Diagram
start
:Open conversation from quote/job context;
:Authorize participant\nrequester / worker / business;
if (Allowed?) then (yes)
  :Compose message;
  if (Attach media?) then (yes)
    :Create media upload;
    :Attach media reference;
  endif
  :Run safety scan\ncontact/payment bypass;
  if (Unsafe?) then (yes)
    :Warn / block / create risk signal;
  else (no)
    :Persist message;
    :Emit MessageSent;
    :Notify recipient;
    :Recipient reads;
    :Mark as read;
    if (Report?) then (yes)
      :Create moderation/support case;
    endif
  endif
else (no)
  :Deny access;
endif
stop

note bottom
Before accepted job/payment state,
phone/email/address/off-platform payment sharing can warn,
soft-block, hard-block or create a risk signal.
end note
@enduml
